@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wtghjm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(0.20))
    v1 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.03 + v2 + 0.07)) / wp.abs((tmp + 0.99 / v2 + 0.10)))
    v2 = (v1 / (v0 / (tmp + 0.67 - v1 + 0.79)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.05) * tmp)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.31)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.14)))
    data[tid] = v0
